Use dark mode styles with:
- Dark backgrounds (#121212, #1e1e1e)
- Light text colors (#ffffff, #e0e0e0)
- Accent colors should have good contrast (min 4.5:1 ratio)
- Avoid pure black backgrounds
- Use subtle shadows for depth
- Consider reducing brightness and saturation of colors
